<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1887-05-11T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1887-05-11T00:00:00-05:00" n="466" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d466">
                    <head>No. 466.<lb/><hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Manning</persName> to Mr. <persName type="to">Bayard</persName>.</hi></head>
                    <opener><seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg></opener>
                    <opener><dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Mexico</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1887-05-11"><hi rend="italic">May</hi> 11, 1887</date>.
                            (Received May 11.)</dateline></opener>
                    <p>Dispatch stating shooting of Nogales rescuers premature.</p>
                    <p>They have appealed.</p>
                    <closer><signed><hi rend="smallcaps">Manning.</hi></signed></closer>
                </div>
                </body></text></TEI>